rows.label: tlk70000035_06_msg0002
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]I really thought my life was
about to starrrrrrrrt!!!

rows.label: tlk70000035_06_msg0003
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]But she was just a Noponnnnnnnnn!!!!!

rows.label: tlk70000035_06_msg0004
rows.name:
...What, isn't she cute, you say?
Well, yeah, sure, she's cute, but...

rows.label: tlk70000035_06_msg0005
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]That's not the kind of cute
that makes me get out of bed
in the morninggggg!!!

rows.label: tlk70000035_06_msg0006
rows.name:
Uh? You never said what species the
girl in question belonged to...?

rows.label: tlk70000035_06_msg0007
rows.name:
W-well... Yeah, OK, I guess all you
said was that there was a "young lady
who wants to join our posse"...

rows.label: tlk70000035_06_msg0008
rows.name:
...Oh God, I'm sorry! It seems
I rushed to conclusions and
got myself too excited.

rows.label: tlk70000035_06_msg0009
rows.name:
Guess I was so keen to move on
from Leon that I let my
imagination run away with me...

rows.label: tlk70000035_06_msg0010
rows.name:
Well, whatever. Rikoko's flute-playing
really is top-notch, so we're back in
the barding business for the long haul!
